name: Breeze Blueberry Zucchini Bread
author: Almond Breeze
summary: This moist quickbread made with Almond Breeze almondmilk combines blueberries and zucchini for summertime deliciousness.
ingredients: ½ cup Almond Breeze Hint of Honey or Vanilla almondmilk
1 ¾ cups shredded zucchini, patted dry between paper towels
directions: Preheat oven to 350 degrees F and coat a loaf pan with nonstick cooking spray
Whisk together sugar, Almond Breeze, vegetable oil, and eggs in a large bowl
Stir together dry ingredients and stir lightly into Almond Breeze mixture
Spread into prepared pan and bake for 1 hour or until a toothpick inserted into the center comes out clean
This bread is best served the next day
